        <num>10-2-8</num>
        <content>
          <p>No person shall misrepresent the price of any commodity or service sold, offered, exposed, or advertised for sale by weight, measure, or count nor represent the price in any manner calculated to, or tending to, mislead or in any way deceive a person.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1972, p. 654, ยง 1.)</p>
